#### CBD drinks and stress levels: Version 3

As for version 1 of this study (20 staff members from the Psychology department), but instead of taking a measurement _only_ on a self-report scale, we took 10 different measures every time point (cortisol levels, blood pressure, heart rate variability, various questionnaires etc).  

